						=image_tag("rose.jpg", id:"#", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Rose Libreri Giovannelli
						%h3 Maid of Honor-Sister of Bride  
						%p One of Lucia's older sisters, Rose has been and is still Lucia's style icon. Although growing up together was sometimes challenging due to stolen hair products, clothing and makeup, their sibling bond has only become stronger. With her amazing cooking skills, Rose can make quinoa taste delicious in any plate! With two children and a seven-year age gap, many still confuse the two of them as twins. (Rose loves it)		
					.item.slide2
						=image_tag("angela.jpg", id:"angela", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Angela Libreri Guttilla
						%h3 Sister of Bride  
						%p Oldest sibling of the Libreri household, Angela has and will always be Mommy #2. Angela is the most nurturing, enthusiastic and reliable person Lucia's ever known. Besides using her hands to make the best pulled pork and heavenly cappuccino cheesecake, Angela's hands are always found on 2 and 10 on the steering wheel at all times, even when her favorite jam comes on the radio.  
					.item.slide4
						=image_tag("irma.jpg", id:"irma", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Irma Cosentino Bondi 
						%h3 Future Sister-In-Law of Bride 
						%p One of the most fun, loud and intellectual accountants ever encountered, Irma is nothing short of a warm hearted individual. Irma loves no chip manicures, hosting awesome house parties and is uncomfortably good at Cards Against Humanity. Lucia couldn't be happier to gain Irma as another older sister. 
					.item.slide5
						=image_tag("laura.jpg", id:"#", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Laura Cosentino  
						%h3 Future Sister-In-Law of Bride 
						%p Many would agree, Laura is the loudest in the Cosentino household. Lucia and Laura share hobbies of revining, drinking Moscato and bargain shopping. Being a cosmetologist, Laura has a passion for the beauty industry and will always manage to keep Lucia's strands of hair in place. Laura has a severe case of cinephilia with the ability to quote any and all movies she's ever watched. Lucia is lucky to gain Laura as a younger sister. 
					.item.slide3
						=image_tag("margaret.jpg", id:"#", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Margaret Trupiano 
						%h3 Cousin of Bride 
						%p More of a sister than a cousin, Margaret has always been Lucia's go-to for laughs, a crying shoulder or a good movie to fall asleep to before it even begins. With a degree in fashion, Lucia likes to consider Margaret as her own personal stylist in desperate moments. Besides sharing their closets, they share an amazing relationship with unforgettable (and some embarrassing) life memories that continue to grow and multiple.
					.item.slide6
						=image_tag("amber.jpg", id:"amber", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Amber Kral
						%h3 Future Sister-In-Law of Bride
						%p Also known as Puppa, Amber is a hugger, a snuggler and an amazing fiancÃ© to Lucia's brother. When she's not mixing drinks behind the bar at Da Luciano's or leaving post-it notes on Lucia's car at work, you'll find Amber whipping up a mean dessert of layered deliciousness, known as Death by Chocolate. 
					.item.slide7
						=image_tag("cristina.jpg", id:"cristina", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Cristina Lorusso 
						%h3 Close Friend of Bride
						%p Girlfriend of Lucia's older brother Pete, Cristina and Lucia have grown close with their common love for food. Lucia has never seen anyone polish more sushi rolls in a matter of minutes and still look as amazing as Cristina does. Besides sushi, Cristina and Lucia also share a love for memes and all things coconut. #nutsforcoconuts
					.item.slide8
						=image_tag("antonietta.jpg", id:"#", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Antonietta Sparacio Libreri 
						%h3 Sister-In-Law of Bride 
						%p If anyone deserves a hug, it's Antonietta. Not only for putting up with one of the Libreri boys, but having enough patience to marry one as well. Her passion for cooking has never failed a hungry stomach in the kitchen. Antonietta has a fun, corky personality and has a talent and passion for drawing. 
					.item.slide9
						=image_tag("rosie.jpg", id:"#", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Rosie Trupiano
						%h3 Cousin of Bride 
						%p One of Lucia's younger cousins, Rosie is a beautiful, fun individual who enjoys playing soccer, singing and spreading nutella on everything (almost as much as Margaret). Rosie can manage to make any selfie look flawless, no filters needed. At family gatherings during the summer, Rosie and Lucia partner in matches of volleyball and dare to challenge any opponents. 
					.item.slide10
						=image_tag("gina.jpg", id:"gina", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Gina Fiorentino
						%h3 Cousin of Bride 
						%p Younger cousin of the bride, Gina is energetic, has a great sense of humor and has a contagious laugh. Gina and Lucia share every Sunday together at Nonna's house eating pasta and sharing stories. Gina has discovered her passion for the fashion industry and can make any manikin look classy from head to toe. Being one of her followers on Instagram and Facebook, Lucia cannot help but idolize this fashionista. 
					.item.slide11
						=image_tag("antonella.jpg", id:"#", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Antonella Accolti
						%h3 Close Friend of Bride
						%p Besides Paolo, Antonella was Lucia's first college soul mate beginning freshman year and they have been inseparable ever since. Antonella enjoys reading Shakespeare, idolizes Marilyn Monroe and is an amazing makeup artist. Not only do Antonella and Lucia share a love for teaching, but they also share a love for the corniest movies (Master of Disguise), weirdest YouTube clips (Marcel the Shell) and frozen yogurt any time of the year (extra toppings please). 
					.item.slide12
						=image_tag("bianca.jpg", id:"#", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Bianca Onrubia 
						%h3 Close Friend of Bride
						%p Otherwise known as B, she is probably the most amazing Filipino you will ever meet in your life. Bianca and Lucia were glued at the hips all through their grammar school years. From sleepovers, camping trips and exchanging nutella sandwiches for Filipino rice for lunch, they have been the closest of friends. Although B and Lucia currently live 92 miles apart from each other, distance has never come between their amazing friendship. 
					.item.slide13
						=image_tag("julia.jpg", id:"#", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Julia Guttilla 
						%h3 Niece of Bride 
						%p Julia is the oldest of Lucia's two nieces. Although she may appear to be shy, Julia is a fun and energetic 8 year old. She loves gymnastics and will make any routine look flawless and painful (for those not flexible). Julia is also the only grandchild that will eat through her entire cannoli clean, and have it refilled by her grandpa, Nonno Luciano.  
					.item.slide14
						=image_tag("eva.jpg", id:"#", :size => '250x250')
						%h2 Eva Guttilla
						%h3 Flower Girl - Niece of Bride 
						%p Eva is Lucia's younger niece who loves warm hugs, glitter and everything sparkly. Her smile is contagious and her charm will melt every heart in the entire room. Eva has an impeccable singing voice, a love for spotlight and has hair that will always manage to cover her entire face, even after multiple attempts of trying to fix it. 
